## Build Halide
In the Halid-dev directory run:

$ cmake -G Ninja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -Wno-dev -S . -B build

to prepare build, then

$ cmake --build build && cmake --install build --prefix Halide-install

## Build Halide examples
From the verification-tests directory run:

$ cmake --build build

Results are found in `even_c.cpp`. In `halide.out` all the debug info is found.